#: ../../../components/mercure.rst:8
msgid ""
"`Mercure`_ is an open protocol allowing to push data updates to web "
"browsers and other HTTP clients in a convenient, fast, reliable and "
"battery-friendly way. It is especially useful to publish real-time "
"updates of resources served through web APIs, to reactive web and mobile "
"applications."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../components/mercure.rst:14
msgid ""
